ActConvention for the Conservation of Salmon in the North Atlantic Ocean
PrecisAppointment of DAVID L. DUNN of Shediac, New Brunswick, to be a Canadian representative to the Council of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; to the North American Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; and to the West Greenland Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization, to serve during pleasure for a term of two years.
